00:24:16.055 --> 00:24:16.680
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:24:20.900 --> 00:24:23.960
JULIAN BEINART:
Anyway, what do you--

00:24:23.960 --> 00:24:28.340
you have a population
in this belt

00:24:28.340 --> 00:24:30.710
on either side of
the border where

00:24:30.710 --> 00:24:37.820
people speak two languages,
share telephone services.

00:24:37.820 --> 00:24:40.910
Industries in one country
