these products.

01:10:17.280 --> 01:10:21.090
The use of the
past selectively--

01:10:21.090 --> 01:10:24.450
for instance, the
operation which

01:10:24.450 --> 01:10:30.060
sent Cuban troops to Angola
to help the African Liberation

01:10:30.060 --> 01:10:32.940
movement was called
Operation Carlota.

01:10:32.940 --> 01:10:35.360
Who is Carlota?

01:10:35.360 --> 01:10:39.630
Carlota was this woman
slave who led the rebellion

01:10:39.630 --> 01:10:41.160
against the United
Fruit Company.

01:10:44.360 --> 01:10:48.050
It was a political move to--

01:10:48.050 --> 01:10:52.490
oh, god, I forgot
about the time.

01:10:52.490 --> 01:10:54.098
This is so interesting.

01:10:57.170 --> 01:10:58.910
Let's just leave it at that.

01:11:05.580 --> 01:11:10.020
The Cuban story has transformed,
of course, since 1978.

01:11:10.020 --> 01:11:14.340
I'm talking about a time
when the pure impulse

01:11:14.340 --> 01:11:19.080
under Soviet
dominance, the change--

01:11:19.080 --> 01:11:25.530
