and so a whole set of things

01:11:25.530 --> 01:11:30.460
which operated at that time.

01:11:33.110 --> 01:11:37.430
Cuba is now a
semi-socialist state,

01:11:37.430 --> 01:11:41.960
opening up to diverse
forms of homeownership,

01:11:41.960 --> 01:11:48.680
property ownership, different
categories of tourism,

01:11:48.680 --> 01:11:49.460
and so on.

